{"obj_edit_time":"1706175289","blocks":[{"block_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf","block_type":1,"children":["doxcnwbdhGSXX0HiaPQ5e18bbTb","MVXkdG6vFoKh0ixQ79BcHKCFnuh","KuKbdHgDqofru1xDC4ycz97cnhc","AUNOd8cCFogoaAxcYu7ciyaenOe","EXA4d6p5So4I4nx7JLnc3msHnfd","Vuf5dhunhoGEB1xdA8IcXp8jn2g","AEpLdZ44voN7WrxT6uhcMfpCnxh","RvAWdjXhcoNrotxJYMrcfHp5nXf","AHV7dZ7e3oyeFCx0qUMc48fGnbc","doxcnnvwZhlcRMhelnLjLTxsQFc","doxcnJg5dJBj9UgCdA9M5DLEi8d","doxcnwbvR8EmoQrZUrm8c3rVlZ2","doxcnQiRyFSHCu5EYliT7IfEqHc","doxcn4J1g7wBvaASLzajAp9w7ag","doxcnPl1D46yfWQmc530Tbqbpec","doxcnryp1u9kqlUJnFNeM4kiKCc","doxcnuRmgPpX1ACLqpaKYze3Yxe","doxcnNUp0IBq8PUE6hv1Egp3yef","doxcnG3Jli8WMjsIKEMx41DuhDh","doxcnZg127K1b9G4xCzR5Mudtcd","doxcn6Q8SfOnZP64udYi8Kc0t8e"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"證券存入-業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxcnwbdhGSXX0HiaPQ5e18bbTb","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"MVXkdG6vFoKh0ixQ79BcHKCFnuh","block_type":2,"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在證券行業，\"轉倉業務\"通常指的是投資者將其持有的證券（股票、債券等）從一個經紀商或帳戶轉移到另一個的過程。這可能是由於多種原因，包括投資策略的變化、經紀商服務的不滿意、費用優勢等。以下是有關證券行業轉倉業務的簡要介紹：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"KuKbdHgDqofru1xDC4ycz97cnhc","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"投資組合調整： 投資者可能會根據市場條件、風險偏好或其他投資目標調整其投資組合。這可能涉及到賣出一些證券並購入其他證券，從而實現投資組合的重新平衡。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"AUNOd8cCFogoaAxcYu7ciyaenOe","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"經紀商選擇： 投資者可能選擇更換經紀商，這可能是因為他們尋求更低的交易佣金、更好的客戶服務、更先進的交易平台或其他因素。在這種情況下，投資者需要將其現有的證券頭寸從原有的經紀商帳戶中轉移到新的帳戶。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"EXA4d6p5So4I4nx7JLnc3msHnfd","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"費用優勢： 不同的經紀商可能對交易收費有所不同。投資者可能會選擇將其證券頭寸轉移到收費更低的經紀商，以減少交易成本。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"Vuf5dhunhoGEB1xdA8IcXp8jn2g","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"地理位置： 投資者有時可能考慮將證券頭寸轉移到更靠近其居住地或業務地點的經紀商，以方便監控和管理投資。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"AEpLdZ44voN7WrxT6uhcMfpCnxh","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"服務不滿意： 投資者可能因為對當前經紀商的服務不滿意而決定轉移其證券頭寸。這可能包括對執行質量、客戶支持或其他服務方面的不滿。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"RvAWdjXhcoNrotxJYMrcfHp5nXf","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"稅務考慮： 在進行證券頭寸的轉倉時，投資者還需要考慮潛在的稅務影響。某些交易可能會觸發資本利得稅，因此投資者可能需要謹慎考慮轉倉的時機，以最小化稅務負擔。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"AHV7dZ7e3oyeFCx0qUMc48fGnbc","block_type":2,"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"總體而言，證券行業的轉倉業務是投資者根據各種因素調整其證券頭寸的一種策略性決策。這需要仔細考慮市場條件、費用結構、服務質量等多個因素，以確保轉倉過程順利進行。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxcnnvwZhlcRMhelnLjLTxsQFc","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"證券存入步驟","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcnJg5dJBj9UgCdA9M5DLEi8d","block_type":2,"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在證券存入過程中，券商主要執行以下關鍵步驟：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxcnwbvR8EmoQrZUrm8c3rVlZ2","block_type":13,"children":["doxcnO63FDriYkaXgbsdJc6ORHe","doxcnaZIlg6oNHQB1XiBRfkQqqh"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"客户准备和教育","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcnO63FDriYkaXgbsdJc6ORHe","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"信息提供：券商需要向客户提供全面的信息，包括即将IPO的公司的背景、财务数据、市场分析和招股说明书。这有助于客户做出更加明智的投资决策。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcnwbvR8EmoQrZUrm8c3rVlZ2"},{"block_id":"doxcnaZIlg6oNHQB1XiBRfkQqqh","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"风险评估教育：券商应教育客户理解新股认购的潜在风险和回报，确保客户对投资的可能结果有一个现实的预期。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcnwbvR8EmoQrZUrm8c3rVlZ2"},{"block_id":"doxcnQiRyFSHCu5EYliT7IfEqHc","block_type":13,"children":["doxcncnSGMIyQfu0usNc04k2Aue","doxcnjfeYvfVNVbYTLnFBajpX0g"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"接收和处理认购订单","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcncnSGMIyQfu0usNc04k2Aue","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"订单收集：券商负责收集客户的认购订单，这包括股票数量和客户愿意支付的最高价格。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcnQiRyFSHCu5EYliT7IfEqHc"},{"block_id":"doxcnjfeYvfVNVbYTLnFBajpX0g","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"确保准确性：券商需要验证订单的准确性，并确保所有的订单都在IPO截止日期前提交。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcnQiRyFSHCu5EYliT7IfEqHc"},{"block_id":"doxcn4J1g7wBvaASLzajAp9w7ag","block_type":13,"children":["doxcn6YNiodXDvrrmAV9X44mJmh","doxcnMTds3f6c4gytCDuEbfxX5d"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"通知客户配售结果","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcn6YNiodXDvrrmAV9X44mJmh","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"配售结果通知：IPO过程结束后，券商应及时通知客户他们是否成功获得新股，以及分配给他们的股票数量。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcn4J1g7wBvaASLzajAp9w7ag"},{"block_id":"doxcnMTds3f6c4gytCDuEbfxX5d","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"处理不成功的申购：对于未能成功配售的客户，券商需要及时处理退款或通知客户未获配股的情况。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcn4J1g7wBvaASLzajAp9w7ag"},{"block_id":"doxcnPl1D46yfWQmc530Tbqbpec","block_type":13,"children":["doxcnBIbMH7AB5D43NwKpIKtd9e","doxcnRlWIVWgqpVYNa9g4vMPEcb"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"执行交易和资金管理","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcnBIbMH7AB5D43NwKpIKtd9e","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"交易执行：对于成功获得新股的客户，券商需要执行股票交易，包括将股票添加到客户的投资组合中。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcnPl1D46yfWQmc530Tbqbpec"},{"block_id":"doxcnRlWIVWgqpVYNa9g4vMPEcb","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"资金处理：管理与新股认购相关的资金流动，确保客户款项的正确扣除和股票的顺利入账。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxcnPl1D46yfWQmc530Tbqbpec"},{"block_id":"doxcnryp1u9kqlUJnFNeM4kiKCc","block_type":2,"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"券商的义务还包括：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxcnuRmgPpX1ACLqpaKYze3Yxe","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"账户审核和合规性确认","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：确保客户账户符合新股认购的要求，进行合规性检查。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcnNUp0IBq8PUE6hv1Egp3yef","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"与IPO承销商协调","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：与承销商协调，确保准确了解配售情况和分配方案。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcnG3Jli8WMjsIKEMx41DuhDh","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"后续服务和支持","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：提供市场信息和投资建议，解答客户的疑问。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcnZg127K1b9G4xCzR5Mudtcd","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"维持合规和记录保持","text_element_style":{"bold":true,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"：确保整个过程符合法规，保持透明的记录以备审计和检查。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf"},{"block_id":"doxcn6Q8SfOnZP64udYi8Kc0t8e","block_type":2,"parent_id":"RxTtdhTtiokV1hxFAZjcMAUWncf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}